    <chapter title="Make block collapsed" id="make-block-collapsed">
        <p>To make the code block collapsible, add the <code>collapsible="true"</code> attribute to the code block.</p>
        <p>By default it will be collapsed, to make it expand add <code>default-state="collapsed"</code> attribute.</p>
        <p>By default, in a collapsed state the first line of the code snippet is used as a title.
            Change it by adding the:</p>
            <list>
                <li><code>collapsed-title</code> attribute to specify a custom title;</li>
                <li><code>collapsed-title-line-number</code> attribute to specify the line to use as the title.</li>
            </list>

